<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-04-27T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-04-27T19:00:00-05:00" n="1394" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1394">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 867.4016/58a</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The</hi>
                            <gloss type="from">
                                <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State</hi>
                            </gloss>
                            <hi rend="italic">to the Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MH1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Morgenthau</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-04-27T19:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">April 27, 1915, 7 p. m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>626. Russian Ambassador has brought to our attention an appeal made by
                            the Catholicos of the Armenian Church that this Government use its good
                            offices with the Turkish Government to prevent the massacre of
                            non-combatant Armenians in Turkish territory.</p>
                        <p>You will please bring the matter to the attention of the government,
                            urging upon it the use of effective means for the protection of
                            Armenians from violence at the hands of those of other religions.</p>
                        <p>The Russian Ambassador calls attention to the fact that there are many
                            Mussulmans in Russian territory and that these enjoy immunity from
                            religious persecution.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_BWJ1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>